rComments: Very engaged and knowledgeable professor; it's clear he is very passionate about Latin American human rights issues, and is very approachable to talk to about both class-related and unrelated topics. Interesting and varied lectures, with heavy readings required before classes.

Loved this class and the way he taught it. Had an immense amount of knowledge on the material and really immersed us in the material. Lots of readings but not all necessary. Strongly recommend this class if you are interested in Latin American history.

Really great prof. In-depth lectures that are useful for evaluations, and the readings he assigns are varied and very interesting. very willing to accommodate any extenuating circumstances and work with students.
